name: Erin to Alba
description: The first CD by trio Party Celtica, containing equal measures of Irish and Scottish-influenced party celtic music. Featuring Lead vocal, Accordion, Mandolin, Tin Whistle and Bass/Keys programming by Richie, powered by Daz's thundering drums and augmented by a share of female lead vocal by Marie, this album represents their 2011/2012 shows. tracks include Pride(in the name of love), Irish Rover, Mull of Kintyre, Tell Me Ma, Loch Lomond, Galway Girl, Shout, 500 Miles and more...

name: Get in 2
description: First CD by multi-instrumental duo, "Get In 2", representing choice material from their Summer 2012 Show. 12 Tracks showing a wide selection of feel-good tastes, instruments and styles. Features acoustic guitars, accordion, bass/keys programming and Lead Vocals by Richie, and thundering drums and lead vocal on two tracks by Daz. Tracks include Go Your Own Way, Happy Together, Every Breath You Take, Dollar, Obladi Oblada, Shang-a-lang, Sing, Tainted Love and more....
